tibble(
  a = Sys.time() + runif(1e3) * 86400,
  b = Sys.Date() + runif(1e3) * 30,
  c = 1:1e3,
  d = runif(1e3),
  e = sample(letters, 1e3, replace = TRUE)
)

Plot

data <- diamonds %>% 
  group_by(cut) %>% 
  count()

ggplot(data, aes(cut, n, fill = cut)) +
  geom_bar(stat = "identity") +
  scale_fill_brewer(palette = "Blues")  +
  theme_minimal()
